1
00:00:00,290 --> 00:00:01,750
So, what are we doing today?

2
00:00:01,750 --> 00:00:05,590
Today is boot camp.
I'm teaching you how to do your own makeup.

3
00:00:05,590 --> 00:00:07,630
Oh! Awesome!

4
00:00:07,630 --> 00:00:09,300
You're surprisingly fired up today.

5
00:00:09,300 --> 00:00:13,760
Actually, during the last class presentation,
I noticed I was a little more confident.

6
00:00:14,850 --> 00:00:16,390
Was it the eyebrows?

7
00:00:16,390 --> 00:00:18,770
The eyebrows and...

8
00:00:18,770 --> 00:00:21,520
And the contacts.
All the compliments probably helped, right?

9
00:00:21,520 --> 00:00:24,820
Speaking in front of everyone...
I guess I wasn't as shy as I used to be.

10
00:00:24,820 --> 00:00:26,110
That's it?

11
00:00:26,110 --> 00:00:28,570
Yeah. For me, that's a huge confidence boost.

12
00:00:28,570 --> 00:00:32,780
Yuki, you're so handsome.
You have trouble with crowds too?

13
00:00:34,200 --> 00:00:36,660
I really can't handle it.

14
00:00:36,660 --> 00:00:39,660
My looks draw too much attention,
so everyone's expectations are sky-high.

15
00:00:39,660 --> 00:00:41,420
The pressure is intense.

16
00:00:41,920 --> 00:00:43,420
It feels like I'm not allowed to fail.

17
00:00:44,130 --> 00:00:48,260
I see.
And here I was, thinking you had life on easy mode.

18
00:00:48,260 --> 00:00:50,840
I can't stand all those eyes on me.
That's why my hands shake.

19
00:00:50,840 --> 00:00:51,680
Sorry about that.

20
00:00:52,930 --> 00:00:56,310
But even if I can't be in the spotlight myself,

21
00:00:56,970 --> 00:00:59,930
I can help someone else shine on stage
with my makeup.

22
00:01:00,190 --> 00:01:01,390
Someone like you, Makoto.

23
00:01:02,270 --> 00:01:03,610
I guess so.

24
00:01:04,400 --> 00:01:07,150
Wow, Yuki. You're beautiful on the inside, too.

25
00:01:07,150 --> 00:01:10,320
What? You're the one who's...

26
00:01:13,410 --> 00:01:16,530
This is the first time
I've talked about this stuff with anyone at college.

27
00:01:16,530 --> 00:01:18,080
This stays between us.

28
00:01:18,080 --> 00:01:21,920
(Wait, he's actually kind of cute.)

29
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,040
And...

30
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:27,210
Thanks for doing the presentation for me.

31
00:01:27,210 --> 00:01:29,210
(Is he... blushing?)

32
00:01:29,210 --> 00:01:33,640
Yuki, you don't... like me, do you?

33
00:01:34,930 --> 00:01:35,970
What are you talking about?
